Speaker 2: Right.

Speaker 1: Okay. Let me go ahead and do that for you. And I can just switch this over to as needed?

Speaker 2: So that means you can order when you feel like it?

Speaker 2: No, I'm good. Just cancel it altogether.

Speaker 1: Okay. Are you canceling it because the pills are not a fit for you or?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Let me make sure you got the right one here. I'm sure you selected the right one.

Speaker 2: Yeah, it was the 100 milligrams, so it doesn't fit at all, whatever, yeah.

Speaker 2: It's exceptional. I'm happy to send you the 10 free pills to try.

Speaker 2: Yeah, but you're not going to charge me every month if I don't like them.

Speaker 1: No, no, no.

Speaker 2: Okay. All right. I'm going to go ahead and send this out to you.

Speaker 1: Okay, very good. We'll get that out to you shortly again. These are the AGVs. It will say AGV on the bottle.

Speaker 1: Okay. It's a single white diamond pill, so when you see it, they might look similar. They're not similar. I'm just giving you a heads up.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: All right. You'll get them in the mail shortly.

Speaker 2: All right. Thank you very much.

Speaker 1: Thank you. Bye-bye.
